The projected climate trends in individual model realizations would results from the superposition of external natural forcings, internal climate variability and the anthropogenic external forcing (i.e. GHG increases), i.e.1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
